’Ł@5ba1373580d65c5de32272593ff27c4496ff0618f2e998b83d4285833a34b7d6ŚTitle: title: attr complete
Path: Examples
Content:
Use another command as completion source.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> def complete-foo [spans: list<string>] {
    [bar baz qux spam eggs] | where $it not-in $spans
}

@complete 'complete-foo'
def foo [...args] { $args }


```
